      "content": "Yeah, though I did get a note from the quality assurance team. They're worried that the Eco-Static models won't be able to handle the complex reasoning or the multi-step logic tasks that you're currently processing. Some of the enterprise clients might see a massive drop in service quality if everything gets pushed to the lightweight models. It's a bit of a trade-off between the energy savings and the performance hit.",
